THE CARE BEAR
why should i care
for my care bear
because he doesn't talk
i might as well talk to my sock
for, he has no mind
no idea to grind
so, why do i talk to my care bear
he has nothing to share
not a word of advice
he wont even eat his pizza slice
his blue color is pretty
and his smile is not too gritty
but it never changes
not even through fazes
but i'll tell you why i care...
this is why i talk to my care bear
and it's not because of his rockin hair
it's because my care bear cares

